Thatâ€™s where a multi-asset approach can help. By combining equity, debt, gold, and silver within one portfolio â€” and adjusting allocations as markets change â€” investors can aim for better diversification and potentially better risk-adjusted returns over the long term.

Live Translation works when paired with an Apple Intelligenceâ€“enabled iPhone running iOS 26 and later. Supports English (UK, U.S.), French (France), German, Portuguese (Brazil), and Spanish (Spain). For more information, see https://www.apple.com/ios/feature-availability/.

00:00 - Introduction to Intraday Trading
01:57 - Understanding Leverage & Risk
03:16 - How to Use Intraday on Groww App

We'll guide you step-by-step on how to place an intraday trade on the Groww app. You'll understand how to use the 5x leverage feature to take larger positions and why it's crucial to manage your risk appetite. We also cover essential topics like squaring off your positions before market close and the availability of Groww's intraday screeners to help you find trading opportunities.

This guide is for anyone in India interested in learning about intraday trading on a popular platform. Always remember to do your own research and understand the risks involved before making any trading decisions.
